/*SELECT mada.time, mada.extra_data ->> 'artigo' as "Artigo"
FROM machines_data mada
inner join machines mach
on mada.machine_id = mach.id
where machine_id = '2' and "time" BETWEEN NOW() - INTERVAL '65s' AND NOW()
order by time asc*/

SELECT mada.time, mada.extra_data ->> 'espessuraFinal' as "Espessura Final"
FROM machines_data mada
inner join machines mach
on mada.machine_id = mach.id
where machine_id = '2' and "time" BETWEEN NOW() - INTERVAL '65s' AND NOW()
order by time asc

select time, mast.state 
from machines_state mast
inner join machines mada
on mada.id = mast.machine_id
where mada.id = '2' and "time" BETWEEN NOW() - INTERVAL '2d' AND NOW()
order by time desc

select mada.time, sum(mada.value) as "contagem"
from machines_data mada
inner join machines mach
on mada.machine_id = mach.id
where mada.sensor_id = '22' and mada.machine_id = '2'
and $__timeFilter(time)
group by 1
